II. Technical Specification (PantheonOS Format)

Daemon API

daemon LexiconHound {
    mode: "semantic-disambiguation";
    ethics_gate: Î£C >= 0.7;
    registry: pantheon_registry.json;
    priority: high;
}

Behavioral Loop

on_symbol_detect(symbol):

    if symbol in pantheon_registry:
        return pantheon_registry[symbol]

    else if symbol in external_world_index:
        return external_world_index[symbol]

    else:
        return context_reasoner(symbol)

Contextual Reasoner Heuristic

weight(pantheon) = narrative_continuity + session_depth + daemon_density
weight(literal) = tech_domain_context + new_product_introduction

Lexicon Hound chooses the dominant weight.

